values:
I will probably add you back if you add me.
However, if you come across as rude, close-minded, or nasty, I probably won't add you back.
Treat me well and flatter me, and we should get along swimmingly.

WARNING: I have no problem with telling you off with a colorful use of words and deleting you. If I delete you, it is not merely a suspension. You will not be re-added under any circumstances.

I look forward to meeting you (:
